parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can cause the occupant to become trapped, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident or emergency situation.

the seat belt buckle is broken
the seat belt buckle is difficult to operate.
